		<div id="comment_body_64967145"><p><div class="quote"><p>Did WSL ever get support for a GUI?  I'm hoping for that<nobr> <wbr></nobr>...</p></div><p>WSL2 has <a href="https://github.com/microsoft/wslg" title="github.com">WSLg</a> [github.com].</p><p>I use it to run Linux IntelliJ IDEA from within WSL and it's not perfect but overall works quite well. The alternative of using Windows IntelliJ IDEA to access a project residing within WSL had very bad performance when I tried it.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64967145">

