		<div id="comment_body_64967637">You like Windows because you were born in Seattle and are a C# programmer, but you like some of the features of Linux (ie, it's easier for development. It comes with half a dozen languages by default, scripting is easier, etc).<br> <br>
Microsoft created WSL as a response to C# programmers deploying their websites into Linux containers on Azure.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64967637">

